Louise Hampton https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Louise_Hampton 0 Louise Hampton (1881 – 11 February 1954) was a British stage, film and television actress.An accomplished stage actress with many West End theatre appearances to her name, she made her film debut in 1911, in the silent thriller Driving a Girl to Destruction. This was the first of many film appearances over the years, often latterly in supporting roles.She was married to Edward Thane.
